{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't walk, I couldn't breathe, and it took quite a few-- a week or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I felt, I don't want to be-- I mean, my father, that time, and there was still my mother's sister there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, do something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get away from here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't be in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I tried to get back to the concentration camp that I worked the summer before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You follow me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Why did you want to go back to the concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that time, we knew that the concentration camps are going to go on a little longer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghettos, we knew they're going to be cleaned out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody tried to get into the concentration camps, because they needed labor, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed people to work on the, on the [INAUDIBLE], on the street, on the roads.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so you know, everybody tried, you know to, to, to, to stretch, to see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe some miracle is going to happen in between.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we know that the, the ghettos are going to be finished off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I gained a little strength and I could start, you know, using my legs again, so I went back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got dressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very cold that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in January or something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- you know, they wouldn't see my face, that they wouldn't, you know, recognize that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started walking through the fields and through the roads, and go back to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I stopped there, and I sleep-- I slept through one or two nights.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, a farmer's house, that he had some, oh, stacks of hay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I got in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I made a little, little, a little hole.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
